{"tid":2077363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2人涉發布西灣河開槍殺人犯資料藐視法庭被捕","createTime":"2020-06-24T08:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T11:36:27.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"81b2ca9b631a78f90d176856ed3df998cf3934ba","tid":2077363,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:35:09.000Z","msg":"2人涉發布西灣河開槍案警員資料藐視法庭被捕<br />\n24.06.2020 16:32<br />\n<br />\n兩名男子涉嫌將西灣河開槍案的警員資料放上社交平台，干犯藐視法庭被捕。<br />\n<br />\n審理開槍案的主任裁判官，本月初下令禁止任何人，報道開槍警員的身份。警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科人員早上在大嶼山及港島，拘捕兩名33及51歲男子，分別報稱無業和社工，涉嫌在社交平台，發布涉案警員的姓名和相片等資料，警方正調查他們循什麼途徑，獲得警員資料，強調不論是自己發放資料，或轉發他人資料，都是違反法庭命令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1318914&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1318914%26csid%3D261_341&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=c0576568\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1318914&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"85bdfb9747271c9c39afe15cb1cb90168ae5e731","tid":2077363,"uid":58841,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:39:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b0e4f0cf3b0460bbfb0058c4f8d5f6211062081","tid":2077363,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:40:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmbxE55hyYzQ&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=e7475fb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ</a>"},{"pid":"72c5410493385f6319ed14354f061e0e05938e57","tid":2077363,"uid":156096,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:40:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f70edee6cc1d3fc89e308e492c165a9d870bf86","tid":2077363,"uid":301666,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,